QUERY_TEXT: CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE analytics.stg_orders AS SELECT id, customer_id, amount, created_at FROM raw.orders WHERE created_at >= '2024-01-01'
CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE analytics.fct_orders AS SELECT o.id, o.amount, c.segment FROM analytics.stg_orders o JOIN analytics.dim_customers c ON o.customer_id = c.id
SELECT segment, SUM(amount) AS total FROM analytics.fct_orders GROUP BY segment
CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE analytics.dim_customers AS SELECT id, name, segment FROM raw.customers
INSERT INTO analytics.stg_orders SELECT id, customer_id, amount, created_at FROM raw.orders WHERE created_at >= '2024-02-01'
